.TH REVIEW_WALLET_IDENTITY_TUI 1 "2026-03-29" "stophammer" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
review_wallet_identity_tui \- interactive review console for pending wallet identity items
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B review_wallet_identity_tui
[
.BI --db " PATH"
] [
.BI --limit " N"
]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B review_wallet_identity_tui
opens a terminal UI for wallet review groups, candidate merges, classification
overrides, and artist-link decisions. It is intended for operators curating the
wallet identity layer after resolver or backfill passes.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BI --db " PATH"
Path to the SQLite database. Defaults to
.BR ./stophammer.db .
.TP
.BI --limit " N"
Maximum number of pending review groups to load. Defaults to 200.
.SH CONTROLS
The interface shows pending wallet groups, candidate wallets, claim feeds, and
evidence branches. Use the on-screen key hints to change focus, expand
evidence, and store durable decisions.
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
Open the TUI against the default database:
.nf
cargo run --bin review_wallet_identity_tui -- --db ./stophammer.db
.fi
.TP
Limit the initial queue size:
.nf
cargo run --bin review_wallet_identity_tui -- --db ./stophammer.db --limit 100
.fi
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR review_wallet_identity (1),
.BR backfill_wallets (1),
.BR stophammer-resolverd (1)
